Vertex Shader:
	The Vertex Position attribute will always be named "position" and its location will be "0";
	The Normal attribute will always be named "normal" and its location will be "1";
	The Texture Coordinates attribute will always be named "tex_coords" and its location will be "2";

	The Color attribute will always be named "color" and its location will be "5";


General:
	Uniform names shall always be prefixed with "u_" (ex: uniform mat4 u_model);